[CITE@@en-US[Internationalization Tag Set (ITS) Version 1.0]] ([TIME[2007-04-03 18:11:18 +09:00]] 版) <http://www.w3.org/TR/2007/REC-its-20070403/#its-version-attribute>
([[名無しさん]])

